name: Z-000_H: @CultureHacker Guest Spot
description: One of the most exciting developments in recent colony history was the discovery of the remains of a data core from a lost probe by Captain Harpee and her crew.  The probeâ€™s core was mostly burnt out but what remains is a tantalising fragment.  It appears to show some kind of sentient creature at the gates of a [Possibly Chinese] colony.  There has been no contact from any other colonies since the British expedition arrived on the planet.
